OL,3,CMark Robins appointed manager of Stoke
OL,4,CCity
OL,6,FThe Sky Blues won the EFL Trophy, were
OL,7,Fpromoted on two occasions, reached the
OL,8,F2023 Championship Playoff Final and
OL,9,Falso reached the semi-final of last
OL,10,Fseason's FA Cup - all under Robins'
OL,11,Fstewardship.
OL,13,FPaul Nevin and James Rowberry,
OL,14,Fcurrently England Under 20s and Wales
OL,15,Fsenior team's Assistant Coach
OL,16,Frespectively, have joined as assistant
OL,17,Fmanagers.
OL,19,FWalters said: "We are delighted to
OL,20,Fwelcome Mark, Paul and James to the
OL,21,FStoke City family.
