OL,3,CMark Robins appointed manager of Stoke
OL,4,CCity
OL,6,F"At Coventry, Mark built something
OL,7,Fsuccessful with a real identity and
OL,8,Flongevity and he left the Club in a
OL,9,Fsignificantly better place than he
OL,10,Ffound it.
OL,12,F"That's exactly what we want to
OL,13,Fachieve at Stoke City, and he has all
OL,14,Fthe pedigree and experience to help us
OL,15,Fdo that.
OL,17,F"With a record like that behind him,
OL,18,FMark was always going to be in great
OL,19,Fdemand, so we're delighted that he
OL,20,Fsees an exciting opportunity to build
OL,21,Fsomething special in the Potteries.
