OL,3,CMark Robins appointed manager of Stoke
OL,4,CCity
OL,6,F"Welcoming two Assistant Managers of
OL,7,Fsuch calibre and with such innovative
OL,8,Fand progressive mindsets in Paul and
OL,9,FJames is another important part of how
OL,10,Fwe will seek to progress and grow.
OL,12,F"The immediate mission is to climb as
OL,13,Fhigh as we can up the Championship
OL,14,Ftable during the second half of this
OL,15,Fseason, whilst also laying foundations
OL,16,Ffor a long-term successful future for
OL,17,Four club."
