OL,4,CCity
OL,6,FChair John Coates said: "With the
OL,7,Fproven track record Mark brings to the
OL,8,Frole, I believe this is a genuinely
OL,9,Fexciting moment for Stoke City.
OL,11,F"The recent win over Sunderland, with
OL,12,Fthe way the team competed on the field
OL,13,Fand connected with the fans, gave
OL,14,Feveryone a huge boost and provided a
OL,15,Fglimpse of what can be created at our
OL,16,Fclub.
OL,18,F"Ryan Shawcross has the sincere thanks
OL,19,Fof us all for the diligent and
OL,20,Finspiring way he has taken to being in
OL,21,Fcaretaker charge.
